      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little TLC. While the engine and transmission are functional, the car shows noticeable wear, including some minor exterior scuffs and interior upholstery thinning. It is currently roadworthy, though it may require upcoming maintenance for items like brake pads and tires to remain in top shape.",
