    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine runs roughly and there are noticeable leaks, while the exterior shows heavy wear including several deep scratches, significant dents, and areas of rust. The interior also shows its age with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. This would be a suitable project car for someone with the time and resources to perform a full restoration.",
